      "description": "## Summary\r\n\r\nThis release introduces a major new feature: an interactive chat interface for conversing with your Obsidian documents.\r\n\r\n## Changes Since v1.1.3\r\n\r\n### New Features\r\n\r\n- **💬 Chat Interface**: Interactive sidebar panel for chatting with documents\r\n  - Real-time streaming responses with markdown formatting\r\n  - Automatic document context inclusion\r\n  - Persistent conversation history across sessions\r\n  - Copy and insert AI responses directly into documents\r\n  - Native Obsidian theming support\r\n  - New ribbon icon (💬) for quick access\r\n  - Commands: \"Open chat\" and \"Toggle chat\"",
